				</div>
				<div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); text-align: left;">
					<h3 style="color:var(--gold); margin-top:0;">Okruhy z√°vozu</h3>
